Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# When I Close My Eyes 當我閉上雙眼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,當我閉上雙眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽見。\NI hear things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,馬車經過時，它的輪子\NThe sound of a carriage passing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟鵝卵石路撞出的聲音。\Nas its wheels wobble against the cobblestone paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我淡出於包裹著我的人群的嘈雜聲。\NI fade softly against the murmurs of the crowds that encompass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,風鈴明明被狂風吹著，\NWooden chimes are faintly heard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,卻沒人聽的到它的聲音。\Nagainst the howling wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽不清。\NUnknown to me.
Comment: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,當我閉上雙眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看見。\NI see things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我看見她，笑著回頭看我，\NI see her smiling back at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我記憶中的那樣，\Njust like I remembered her doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是多麼遙遠，當時事情還沒這麼複雜。\Nlong ago when things were simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我看見我，在鏡子裡面，\NI see myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上作夢時，我知道鏡子裡的是我，\NIn my dreams, I know it's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,白天醒著時，我卻是開始懷疑自己。\Nbut in the daylight, I can never be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,艷麗的青與赤在天上飛舞，但老實說，再怎麼美麗，\NBrilliant blues and pinks cascade across a sky that, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我都從沒抬頭看過。\NI never look up at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好特別的。\NThis is nothing profound.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,當我閉上雙眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我夢見。\NI dream of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們只不過\NBut they're only familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,僅只於\Nto the point
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中\Nof a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,的感受。\Nthat I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我閉上雙眼，\NI close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在花凋葉落前我都不要醒來。\Nand dream until every petal falls.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,## 尾奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,當我閉上雙眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我試著忘記張眼時的感覺。\NI try to forget what it's like to keep them open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,當我閉上雙眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我試著忘記他們的責罵。\NI try to forget the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,當我閉上雙眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我試著記好我的名字。\NI try to remember my name.
